mixin menucontent(options)

	- buttonClass = 'small';

	.aside__avatar
		+img({
			src:'avatars/avatar.jpg',
			width:'120',
			height:'120',
			alt:'avatar',
			lazy: 'false'
		})
	.aside__legend
		| David Baker
		.small
			| Frontend Developper
	.aside__social-links
		+button({
			type:'icon',
			icon:'skype-with-circle',
			classes: buttonClass,
			href:'#',
			target: '_self'
		})
		+button({
			type:'icon',
			icon:'github-with-circle',
			classes: buttonClass,
			href:'#'
		})
		+button({
			type:'icon',
			icon:'linkedin-with-circle',
			classes: buttonClass,
			href:'#'
		})
		+button({
			type:'icon',
			icon:'twitter-with-circle',
			classes: buttonClass,
			href:'#'
		})
	.aside__legend
		.small
			| A blog about coding, programming and various things. Build on NodeJs using ExpressJS, Jade and Db'ing in MongoDB
